OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLots of late
OL,6,Fevening sunshine to finish the day.
OL,7,FRemaining dry and warm across the
OL,8,Fregion perhaps with a few patches of
OL,9,Flow cloud in the east. Remaining
OL,10,Frather breezy, if not windy, along
OL,11,Fsouthern coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FAnother very hot, sunny day
OL,14,Fwith brisk winds. Perhaps the odd
OL,15,Fafternoon shower. Windy around coasts,
OL,16,Fso take care if you plan on taking a
OL,17,Fdip at the beach.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
