OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FRemaining largely dry, hot and sunny
OL,7,Fin the outlook. However, the chance of
OL,8,Fa few showers and the odd
OL,9,Fthunderstorm. Brisk winds remain along
OL,10,Fcoastlines.
